<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>This is a request for validate classes that are like Alpha and Alnum, but which also permit whitespace.</p>

<p>So values like "1313 Mockingbird Lane" can be validated.</p>

<p>Suggested class names:</p>

<ul><li>Zend_Validate_AlphaWS</li>
<li>Zend_Validate_AlnumWS</li>
</ul>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="comments">
